### Sweet Treats Bakery
Fresh homemade sweets and treats!

## Doughnut Flavours

All our doughnuts are made fresh daily without preservatives and are best enjoyed immediately.

* Strawberry sugar doughnuts
* White cream filled chocolate dipped doughnuts
* Old fashioned cinnamon sugar doughnuts
* Chocolate glazed doughnuts
* Old fashioned glazed doughnuts



## Our Specialties

* Triple Chocolate Brownies | Chocolate lovers delight decadently delicious
* Blueberry Kuchen | Delicious 6" coffee cakes perfect for 2-3
* Apple Bread | Delicious 6" coffee cakes perfect for 2-3
